These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: lily, iris, poppy, balloon-flower, marigold, dahlia
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, ship, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the person driving the scooter is the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the taxi##2
5. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
8. the person who growsdahlia is the person driving the skateboard##1
9. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Flower         | marigold     | poppy | lily | balloon-flower | dahlia      | iris |
| Transport   | snowmobile | taxi  | scooter    | tram | skateboard | ship    |

