.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, horror, mystery, satire, scientific, time-travel
6 different pets are kept: horse, chinchilla, turtle, goat, dog, mouse
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the goat##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | satire  | scientific | horror   | time-travel | mystery |
| Pet   | turtle | dog | chinchilla    | mouse | horse   | goat   |

