.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: brazilian, malaysian, spanish, pakistani, polish, colombian
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, golf, handball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the spanish##3
4. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
5. the colombian is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
6. the polish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the malaysian##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's sport is handball is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | polish | spanish     | malaysian         | pakistani       | colombian     |
| Sport         | basketball | golf  | cycling | weightlifting | ice-hockey | handball |

