.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, volleyball, golf, soccer, baseball
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, skateboard, train, tram, van
1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
9. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Sport   | badminton | cycling     | volleyball     | golf | soccer | baseball |
| Transport     | van    | motorbike | skateboard | train  | tram       | boat      |

