.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, romance, scientific, time-travel, western
The people have 6 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, singing, collecting, photography, camping
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 2. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 8. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
11. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific | documentary | western    | romance    | musical |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks         | traveling       | singing  | collecting | photography | camping   |

