 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is the russian##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
10. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |
