.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-10::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: purple, grey, blue, black, aquamarine, ivory
The people use 6 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, scooter, ship, train, van
 1. the person driving the ship is between the person who likes blue and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the person who likes grey##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 9. the person who likes purple is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
11. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Color    | purple | black | blue | ivory | aquamarine      | grey    |
| Transport   | train       | van      | quad-bike     | ship  | motorbike | scooter |

