 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person eating onion and the person watching scientific movies##2
10. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating pear##1
11. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

